","Abt 1094":"about 1094","about 1166":"about 1166","about 1120":"about 1120","South Newington, Oxfordshire, England":"South Newington, Oxfordshire, England","Of, South Newington, Oxfordshire, England":"South Newington, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","England":"England","Deddington, Oxfordshire, England":"Deddington, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom","Heyford Warren, Oxfordshire, England":"Heyford Warren, Oxfordshire, England","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Bereford","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["English: habitational name from a place in the parish of Alstonfield, Staffordshire named Beresford, from Old English <i>beofor</i> ‘beaver’ (or possibly from a byname from this word) + Old English <i>ford</i> ‘ford’. This name also became established in Ireland.","History: The first recorded bearer of the surname is John <i>de Beveresford</i>, who held the manor of Beresford, Staffordshire, from <i>c.</i> 1220 to 1241. All present-day Beresfords are apparently descended from Thomas Beresford, who fought at Agincourt in 1415 and who fathered sixteen sons and five daughters. The Irish branch of the family includes the Marquesses of Waterford."],"variants":[{"name":"Berisford","meanings":["English: variant of   Beresford  ."]}]},{"name":"Denise","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["feminine form of   Denis  , widely used in the English-speaking world since the 1920s.  See also  Dionysia ."],"variants":[{"name":"Denyse","meanings":["feminine form of   Denis  , widely used in the English-speaking world since the 1920s.  See also  Dionysia ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Denise Bereford was born about 1094, in England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Walkelin Ward de Bereford. She married Hugh de Chesney of Graffham & Ducklington. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 2 daughters. She died about 1166, in Deddington, Oxfordshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 74."},"et":{"Abt 1094–Abt 1166":"umbes 1094–umbes 1166","1094–1166":"1094–1166","1107–1166":"1107–1166","1120–1196":"1120–1196","1126–1204":"1126–1204","1145–1200":"1145–1200","1163–1213":"1163–1213","1076–1142":"1076–1142","1142":"1142","1076":"1076","1120":"1120","Abt 1126":"umbes 1126","1163":"1163","1196":"1196","1094":"1094","1107":"1107","1204":"1204","1126":"1126","1213":"1213","1145":"1145","Abt 1166":"umbes 1166","1200":"1200","1166":"1166","Abt 1094":"umbes 1094","about 1166":"umbes 1166","about 1120":"umbes 1120","South Newington, Oxfordshire, England":"South Newington, Oxfordshire, England","Of, South Newington, Oxfordshire, England":"South Newington, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","England":"England","Deddington, Oxfordshire, England":"Deddington, Oxfordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Heyford Warren, Oxfordshire, England":"Heyford Warren, Oxfordshire, England"},"fi":{"Abt 1094–Abt 1166":"noin 1094–noin 1166","1094–1166":"1094–1166","1107–1166":"1107–1166","1120–1196":"1120–1196","1126–1204":"1126–1204","1145–1200":"1145–1200","1163–1213":"1163–1213","1076–1142":"1076–1142","1142":"1142","1076":"1076","1120":"1120","Abt 1126":"noin 1126","1163":"1163","1196":"1196","1094":"1094","1107":"1107","1204":"1204","1126":"1126","1213":"1213","1145":"1145","Abt 1166":"noin 1166","1200":"1200","1166":"1166","Abt 1094":"noin 1094","about 1166":"noin 1166","about 1120":"noin 1120","South Newington, Oxfordshire, England":"South Newington, Oxfordshire, England","Of, South Newington, Oxfordshire, England":"South Newington, Oxfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Oxfordshire, England":"Oxfordshire, England","England":"England","Deddington, Oxfordshire, England":"Deddington, Oxfordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Heyford Warren, Oxfordshire, England":"Heyford Warren, Oxfordshire, England"},"fr":